    "We argue that it is because the structural function employed in this benchmark lies in the \"good\" regime.",
    "Utilising the alignment estimation methods outlined in Section 5, we are able to provide evidence for this claim.",
    "We observe that the structural function is spanned by the leading singular functions of the conditional expectation operator associated with this model.",
